  - m_Id: 864226270014
    m_Localized: Unload
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270015
    m_Localized: Vehicle Assembly Plant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270101
    m_Localized: A chemical processing facility. Consumes crude oil to produce fabric,
      enabling textile production without relying solely on wood.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270102
    m_Localized: A general parts factory. Produces machine parts from iron ingots.
      Foundational mid-game facility for engines and vehicles.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270103
    m_Localized: An engine factory. Consumes machine parts, electronic components,
      and steel ingots to produce engines. A prerequisite for vehicle assembly.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270104
    m_Localized: A heavy luxury factory. Produces premium clothing from fabric and
      gold ore, and premium furniture from premium wood, fabric, and machine parts.
      High investment for high-value goods.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270105
    m_Localized: A light consumer-goods factory. Produces basic furniture from fine
      wood and machine parts, basic clothing from fabric, and simple tools from iron
      ingots and fine wood. Switch product lines to match demand.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270106
    m_Localized: A loading station where resources are picked up from storage and
      loaded onto the production line. Workers efficiently transfer materials to
      begin the manufacturing process.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270116
    m_Localized: A logging camp that harvests raw timber from nearby forests. Produces
      logs without consuming any auxiliary materials. First step in the wood production
      chain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270108
    m_Localized: A military factory. Produces small arms from steel, fine wood, and
      machine parts; heavy arms from steel and machine parts; and munitions from
      steel and coal. High demand during wartime.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270109
    m_Localized: A dedicated iron ore mine. Extracts iron ore for smelting into iron
      ingots. Core facility for metalworking chains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270110
    m_Localized: An oil drilling facility that extracts crude oil from underground
      reserves. Essential for fuel production and chemical processing. Requires high
      maintenance costs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270111
    m_Localized: A transportation pathway that connects different areas of the production
      line. Essential infrastructure for moving resources and products efficiently
      between facilities.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270112
    m_Localized: A sawmill. Consumes wood logs to produce fine wood, and fine wood
      to produce premium wood. Most efficient when supplied from a nearby Logging
      Camp.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270113
    m_Localized: A smelter. Converts iron, copper, and aluminum ores into ingots,
      and gold ore into pure gold. Essential for metalworking and electronics chains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270114
    m_Localized: An unloading station where finished products are removed from the
      production line and stored. Workers carefully handle completed items for inventory
      management.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270115
    m_Localized: A vehicle assembly plant. Produces cars, fighter jets, and battle
      tanks using engines, steel, electronics, aluminum, oil, and weapons depending
      on the design.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270201
    m_Localized: Distribution
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270202
    m_Localized: Production
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22446163628539904
    m_Localized: Raw Production
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270016
    m_Localized: Splitter
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270117
    m_Localized: Splits incoming resources into two lanes. At base rotation it alternates output to the right and downward lanes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270017
    m_Localized: Tunnel
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270118
    m_Localized: A two-lane pass-through road. Vertical and horizontal traffic are buffered separately and move without blocking each other.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270018
    m_Localized: Gold Mine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270119
    m_Localized: A dedicated gold mine. Extracts gold ore only for smelting into
      pure gold. Higher cost than a general mine; placement may be limited.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270020
    m_Localized: Electronic Components Factory
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270120
    m_Localized: Produces electronic components from copper and aluminum ingots. Required
      for engines and advanced production chains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270021
    m_Localized: Coal Mine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270121
    m_Localized: A dedicated coal mine. Extracts coal for smelting, fuel, and munitions
      production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270022
    m_Localized: Copper Mine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270122
    m_Localized: A dedicated copper ore mine. Extracts copper ore for smelting and
      electronics chains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270023
    m_Localized: Aluminum Mine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270123
    m_Localized: A dedicated aluminum ore mine. Extracts aluminum ore for smelting
      and advanced manufacturing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
